data.text:
A pretty, detailed print of my hand-drawn illustration of the most famous landmarks in Newport, Wales.

Great as a gift for anyone from Newport, or as a gift for someone moving to or from Newport. It could also make a wonderful engagement or wedding gift.

My Newport illustration was drawn using pen and ink, by hand, and has then been digitally manipulated to come up with the final image. It features Newport Castle, the Civic Centre, Tredegar House, Newport Cathedral, Celtic Manor, Caerleon Amphitheatre, the 'In the Nick of Time' clock, The Wave and the Transporter Bridge.

Add a coloured background and/or a line of personalised text to really customise your print.

The standard print is approx 210mm x 300mm and fits into any off the shelf A4 sized frame. The large print is approx 300mm x 420mm and will fit into an A3 frame.

It's printed digitally onto high quality archival paper which will not fade or discolour. It will arrive unframed, in a hardbacked envelope.

Also available as a card or as wedding or party invites.

Please note that the frame in the photos is not included.
